⍝ map + fold: build a list [0..999], map, then fold. No output.

nums ← ⟪
  ⟲ (Step•(0 [])) ▷ ⟪
  ▷ Done•xs     ⇒ ↯ xs
  ▷ Step•(i xs) ⇒ ↩ (
        (i ≥ 1000) ▷ ⟪
        ▷ ⊤ ⇒ Done•xs
        ▷ ⊥ ⇒ Step•(i + 1  xs ⊞ [i])
        ⟫
      )
  ⟫
⟫

inc ← ⌁(x) x + 1
ys ← map · inc · nums
fold · (⌁(a b) a + b) · 0 · ys
